程序包 projecttwo

类 MemberDatabase

java.lang.Object
projecttwo.MemberDatabase
public class MemberDatabase extends Object
The MemberDatabase is the class that will store the Member object. It is a sequenceList datastructures.

author: Michael Israel, Kangwei Zhu

  • 构造器详细资料

    • MemberDatabase

      public MemberDatabase()
      Initialize a newly created MemberDatabase object. Initialize MemberDatabase's Member array mlist to an empty array with size 4. And set the number of members to 0.

  • 方法详细资料

    • find

      private int find(Member member)
      This method is for finding whether a Member object exists in this MemberDatabase object.
      参数:
      member - a specific Member object.
      返回:
      Index of this Member in mlist if this Member does exist. If it not exists, return -1.

    • contains

      public int contains(Member member)
      This method is for check whether the MemberDataBase contains a specific Member object.
      参数:
      member - a specific Member object.
      返回:
      Index of this Member in mlist if this Member does exist. If it not exists, return -1.

    • getMember

      public Member getMember(Member member)
      This method is used when retrieving a member from the database
      参数:
      member - The member that we want to retrieve.
      返回:
      null if not found, otherwise the Member Object.

    • grow

      private void grow()
      Increase the amount of Member object that the database could store by 4.

    • getSize

      public int getSize()
      Get the number of Member object that currently stored in this database.
      返回:
      number of Member object stored in this database.

    • add

      public boolean add(Member member)
      Add a Member object into the database. To successfully add a Member object, the database must not contain this Member object.
      参数:
      member - Member object that going to be added.
      返回:
      true if this Member is add successfully, false if this Member object has already been added.

    • remove

      public boolean remove(Member member)
      Remove a Member object in database. To remove this Member object, the database must have this object.
      参数:
      member - Member object that going to be removed.
      返回:
      true if this Member has been successfully removed, false otherwise.

    • print

      public void print()
      Print all the Member objects that are currently stored in database

    • printByType

      public void printByType(Member curMember)
      This method is used when displaying/printing the member by its membership Types. This is because for Premium membership and Family membership, we need to print their number of guest pass.
      参数:
      curMember - The input member that are going to be displayed.

    • printSchedule

      public void printSchedule()
      Print all the Member objects that are currently stored in database. Notice that this method is used for printing the all the members in one specific fitness database.

    • printByCounty

      public void printByCounty()
      Sort the database Member objects by county name, if county name is equal, then sort by zipcode.

    • printByExpirationDate

      public void printByExpirationDate()
      Sort the database Member objects by its expiration date.

    • printByName

      public void printByName()
      Sort the database Member objects by its first name and last name. First check first name, then check last name.

    • printByMembershipFees

      public void printByMembershipFees()
      Print the current list with the membership Fees. (for next billing statement and regardless the expiration date)
